{"word":"G3594 - ὁδηγέω - hodēgéō - hod-ayg-eh'-o - Guide","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὁδηγέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hodēgéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hod-ayg-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Guide</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - வழிகாட்டு, வழிநடத்து"},{"paragraph":"to be a guide, lead on one's way, to guide"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3595 - ὁδηγός - hodēgós - hod-ayg-os'/3595\">G3595</a>; to <i>show</i> the <i>way</i> (literally or figuratively [<i>teach</i>]): - guide, lead.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1327/1327\">G1327</a>, <a href=\"#/G1529/1529\">G1529</a>, <a href=\"#/G1841/1841\">G1841</a>, <a href=\"#/G3180/3180\">G3180</a>, <a href=\"#/G3594/3594\">G3594</a>, <a href=\"#/G3595/3595\">G3595</a>, <a href=\"#/G3598/3598\">G3598</a>"}]}